&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We notice that although \(\lvert{CG}\rvert\) should have been constant, it is not. Probably the measurement of my reference drill bit collar depth \(\lvert{AD}\rvert\) is not accurate enough. This value varies from \(\frac{21}{32}\) to \(\frac{23}{32}\), thus since this is a constant, I will be using the following value moving forward:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;stemblock&#34;&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;content&#34;&gt;
\[\begin{array}{rcl}
\lvert{CG}\rvert &amp;amp;\approx&amp;amp; \frac{22}{32}
\end{array}\]
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
